outside county of publication:
regular rate, 12.4 cents to 30.2 cents per pound and 4.9 cents to 16.0 cents per piece. up from 11.8 cents to 28.9 cents per pound and 3.8 cents to 12.3 cents per piece
nonprofit, 8.6 cents to 22.1 cents per pound and 3.8 cents to 12.5 cents per piece. changed from 8.5 cents to 28.3 cents per pound and 3.2 cents to 8.7 cents per piece
_third class (advertising):
single piece, 25 cents to $1.50. up from 22 cents to $1.38
bulk rate, 16.7 cents. up from 12.5 cents
