the majority of people living in the region are armenian, but it is part of the republic of azerbaijan. armenians are demanding that it be made part of neighboring armenia
people aren't even thinking of going to work,'' said the resident, a man answering the telephone at the sovietsky karabakh newspaper. he refused to give his name or position
